public abstract class AbstractNBWLikeAcc<A extends AbstractNBWLikeAcc<A>>
extends AbstractSetAcc<State,​StateSet,​StateList,​StateRun,​A>
This class provides a category of acceptance conditions of which each condition is a set of states. Büchi condition, classic condition, and co-Büchi condition belong to this category.
